<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2024-02-20 22:09:30.134888</lastBuildDate><item><title>As Monday's go this was the shittiest!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NOnAfN8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9myA8Nm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wasn't going to post about it but there is something to be said about screaming into the void! I really am having a difficult time dealing with all of it.

This was not something I expected to make most viral. I just needed to get shit off my chest.

Ok, so obviously I couldn't sleep a wink last night, I took all your great advice and researched my state and it turns out y'all are right. So I emailed HR and told them I didn't think their policy and my write up was legal.

UPDATE: I Had my meeting with HR and they said their policy was in place to protect employees from someone who might further injure a downed employee if they don't know what they are doing...right. I told them that the policy isn't legal and employees shouldn't be reprimanded or punished for rendering first aid. We went back and forth on it and they finally agreed to remove my write ups. I also found out that we do have a Defibrillation that myself and very few people know about it. Then I suggested we train an emergency response team in CPR and basic first aid and they seemed interested so I guess we'll see.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NOnAfN8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Iblamemyparentstoo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fashionistas, yea or nay?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5n0FpG3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zeJYTEh.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5n0FpG3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My 15th Favorite</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HpHl297</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yAJtneS.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>and a link to the original https://imgur.com/gallery/pICfPnI</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HpHl297</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Altanese]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Snow zoomies upset neighbors ....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/G4Le27O</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8gOjQf5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/G4Le27O</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Herebychoice]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Boyfriend? Future husband if you ask me.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aXWkonN</link><descri